  "title": "Sales Telemarketer (BEAUTY INDUSTRY with HIGH COMMISSION) 5Day !",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Contact potential and existing clients to promote skincare products and services, schedule appointments, follow up on sales, and gather customer feedback to support business growth and customer satisfaction.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Contact potential and existing clients via phone to promote skincare products, treatments, and services</li><li>Explain clearly the benefits of beauty and skincare products, treatments, and ongoing promotions to customers</li><li>Schedule consultations, product demonstrations, or treatment appointments with beauty consultants</li><li>Conduct follow-up calls to handle customer enquiries and encourage repeat purchases</li><li>Achieve and exceed daily, weekly, and monthly sales or lead generation targets</li><li>Collect customer feedback on products and services and report insights to management</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in telemarketing, sales, or customer service, preferably in the beauty or skincare industry</li><li>Strong verbal communication and active listening skills to build rapport over the phone</li><li>Confident persuasion and negotiation skills to pitch products and close sales</li><li>Effective time management skills to handle a high volume of calls and complete follow-up tasks</li><li>Customer-focused mindset to understand customer needs and recommend suitable solutions</li><li>Proficient in spoken Chinese to communicate with Chinese-speaking clients</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Location: 111 Somerset Road, #06-06 TripleOne Somerset, Singapore 238164</li><li>Working Hours: Monday to Friday, 9:00am – 6:00pm</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong>: Stable and growing Singapore-based beauty company Supportive team environment with performance-based rewards High commission structure with attractive earning potential Convenient central office location (5-minute sheltered walk from MRT)</p><p><strong>Staff Benefits:</strong> Birthday Leave Medical Insurance Coverage Leave entitlements in accordance with MOM requirements Welcome Lunch, team bonding activities, and festive/event celebrations</p><ul><li>Find out more at [apexretail.com.sg](https: //apexretail.com.sg)</li></ul>",
